Where are you?"

1134
00:59:34.067 --> 00:59:35.568
And I was. like.
"I'm in Highland Park."

1135
00:59:36.403 --> 00:59:39.113
He was. like. "No..."

1136
00:59:39.114 --> 00:59:41.532
As for the next
