- It's Friday.

1250
01:06:12.840 --> 01:06:14.592
- I know.
- Friday.

1251
01:06:14.967 --> 01:06:16.468
Oh. shit.

1252
01:06:16.469 --> 01:06:20.430
Ruth. I may not have
this opportunity again.

1253
01:06:20.431 --> 01:06:21.640
He never sees anyone.

1254
01:06:21.641 --> 01:06:23.642
You may not have
this opportunity again?

1255
01:06:23.643 --> 01:06:25.310
- I don't know.
- Yeah. you're right.

1256
01:06:25.311 --> 01:06:26.603
So be home by 7:00
or you will miss

1257
01:06:26.604 --> 01:06:29.648
your own fucking engagement
party. like...

1258
01:06:29.649 --> 01:06:31.901
Right. Of course. Of course.

1259
01:06:33.236 --> 01:06:34.695
Okay.

1260
01:06:34.696 --> 01:06:36.197
I love you. by the way.

1261
01:06:40.493 --> 01:06:41.577
I'm gonna call you back.

1262
01:06:43.913 --> 01:06:45.665
Package for Mr. Redfellow.

1263
01:06:59.637 --> 01:07:00.680
Remember to breathe.

1264
01:07:01.681 --> 01:07:02.682
Very important.

1265
01:07:11.899 --> 01:07:13.025
