by the FBI.

1275
01:07:48.853 --> 01:07:50.313
And yet here you are.

1276
01:07:51.355 --> 01:07:52.606
It's almost as if.
I don't know.

1277
01:07:52.607 --> 01:07:53.858
they don't quite have a case.

1278
01:07:55.485 --> 01:07:57.153
Which is bananas.

1279
01:07:59.739 --> 01:08:02.492
Anyway. I will need
a down payment.

1280
01:08:04.035 --> 01:08:06.703
