1281
01:08:06.704 --> 01:08:07.704
Shit.

1282
01:08:07.705 --> 01:08:09.331
I'm done
fucking around.

1283
01:08:09.332 --> 01:08:10.624
It's...

1284
01:08:10.625 --> 01:08:11.750
You gotta be shitting me.

1285
01:08:11.751 --> 01:08:13.627
You still have a company
checkbook. right?

1286
01:08:13.628 --> 01:08:15.838
You still have access
